content: How much do I owe in taxes?

Tax rate,Taxable income threshold
3.50%, on the portion of taxable income that is $14680 or less, plus
4.40%, on the portion of taxable income over $14680 up to $29370 plus
5.30%, on the portion of taxable income over $29370 up to $323290 plus
7.65%, on the portion of taxable income over $323290
